                <head>Students of the Concordia Society</head>
                <note rend="inline" rendition="#center" type="source">[Translation.]</note>
                <dateline>
                    <placeName>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Berne</hi>
                    </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1865-05-03">
                        <hi rend="italic">May</hi> 3, 1865</date>.</dateline>
                <p>The students of the Concordia Society, 19 members, have this day resolved to
                    unite in the address of sympathy and condolence to the American Union. In the
                    name of the Concordia:</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <list>
                            <item>A. SCHEURER, <hi rend="italic">President, Law Student</hi>.</item>
                            <item>BERGER, <hi rend="italic">Secretary</hi>.</item>
                        </list>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
